    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible, flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been meticulously cared for, kept in a garage, and it's sparkling inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it!",
