    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD in museum-quality condition. This chassis retains its factory-spec 13B-REW rotary powerplant, exhibiting optimal compression across all rotor faces. The sequential twin-turbocharger system transitions seamlessly at 4,500 RPM, delivering linear torque through the 5-speed manual gearbox and Torsen limited-slip differential. The double-wishbone suspension remains tight, preserving the legendary 50/50 weight distribution and neutral handling characteristics. With zero vacuum line degradation and pristine interior surfacing, this is a turn-key example of 90s JDM engineering at its zenith.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
