    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a truly exceptional 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman in a condition that can only be described as showroom-fresh. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained within a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a rainy day. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a high-end ceramic coating that delivers a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no swirl marks or stone chips. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and every electronic component functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by authorized technicians. It features a clean title, no accident history, and has never been tracked. For the buyer seeking a turn-key, collector-grade sports car that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line, this is the one.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
