      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total gem? I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014always garage-kept, meticulously cleaned, and it drives like a total dream. No scratches, no surprises, just a pristine ride waiting for its next adventure. You really won't find another one this clean out there. Come by and see it for yourself, you're going to love it!",
